<p><strong>WHEREAS</strong>, Maryland voters must have confidence that elections are conducted lawfully, securely, and uniformly, and that only eligible voters are registered and permitted to cast ballots; and</p>
<p><strong>WHEREAS</strong>, the General Assembly of Maryland has considered legislation known as the <em>Secure the Vote Act of 2026</em>;</p>
